These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: milk, iced-tea, coffee, fanta
Sport: badminton, parkour, rugby, swimming
1. Beverage:milk is on the right of Sport:rugby##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the far left##1
3. Sport:rugby is between Sport:parkour and Beverage:iced-tea##2
4. Beverage:fanta is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:coffee is between Beverage:iced-tea and Beverage:milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta         | iced-tea   | coffee | milk       |
| Sport      | swimming | badminton | rugby   | parkour |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: hiking, cooking, puzzles, dancing
Nationality: australian, mexican, argentine, canadian
1. Nationality:canadian is between Hobby:puzzles and Nationality:mexican##2
2. Hobby:dancing is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:argentine is on the right of Nationality:australian##1
4. Hobby:hiking is on the left of Nationality:australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | cooking | hiking | puzzles | dancing |
| Nationality   | mexican    | canadian   | australian | argentine       |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Food: pepper, potato, watermelon, carrot
Nationality: turkish, nigerian, russian, spanish
