2. Nationality:russian is between Nationality:nigerian and Food:potato##2
3. Nationality:nigerian is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:spanish is on the left of Food:watermelon##1
5. Food:potato == Nationality:spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | carrot    | pepper | potato   | watermelon  |
| Nationality   | nigerian | russian   | spanish | turkish |

